OL,3,CFirefighters battling wildfires in
OL,4,CElan Valley for fourth day
OL,6,FFirefighters have entered their fourth
OL,7,Fday of battling several wildfires in
OL,8,Fand around Elan Valley.
OL,10,FCrews have been working at popular
OL,11,Fbeauty spots to try and stop wildfires
OL,12,Fspreading since Sunday, April 26.
OL,14,FThe Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService has urged people to avoid the
OL,16,Farea to allow emergency services to
OL,17,Frespond to the fires.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
