OL,3,CFirefighters battling wildfires in
OL,4,CElan Valley for fourth day
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,Fservice said: "Since Sunday, April 26,
OL,8,FMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService crews have responded to
OL,10,Fseveral wildfires in and around the
OL,11,FElan Valley area.
OL,13,F"Firefighter crews are continuing to
OL,14,Frespond to fires near the Claerwen Dam.
OL,16,F"The area should be avoided while this
OL,17,Fincident is ongoing to allow access
OL,18,Ffor emergency services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
