OL,3,CFirefighters battling wildfires in
OL,4,CElan Valley for fourth day
OL,6,F"Local residents are advised to keep
OL,7,Fwindows and doors closed if there is
OL,8,Fthick smoke in the area."
OL,10,FIn 2025, 3,474 grass fires were
OL,11,Fattended by firefighters in Wales,
OL,12,Fwhich is an almost 300% increase from
OL,13,Fthe year before. Deliberate grass
OL,14,Ffires rose to over 2,000, which is an
OL,15,Fincrease of over 250% since 2024.
OL,17,FThe Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService has urged the public to be
OL,19,Fcareful during this time year as fires
OL,20,Fon dry land can quickly turn into
OL,21,Fwildfires.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
